2 Lyon Park Road, North Ryde is inspirational multi award winning A-grade office building located in the premier business district of North Ryde.

2 Lyon Park Road, North Ryde offers the tenant a unique office building with character and style. Features include:
- Abundance of natural light
- Balconies on all levels
- 3 levels undercover security parking
- Environmentally responsible design
- Security access to all floors
- Walking distance to Macquarie Shopping Centre & proposed Macquarie University Rail Station
- Currently for lease is a suite on level 3 which offers a premium position opposite the elevator and excellent levels of natural light from the 3rd floor position. This suite is available from July 2008 and sizes can range from 500-1,100sqm.

Located in the heart of North Ryde, approximately 200m from the intersection of Julius Ave and Delhi Road.

2 Richardson Place is the home to Ricoh, Honeywell and Paynter Dixon.

The fantastic location offers a pleasant walk to the North Ryde Station, close proximity to the Village Green amenities in addition to an on-site caf√©.

Available for lease:
+ Whole 3,755sqm floor plate, with great natural light
+ Complete near new fitout in place, providing versatility to suit a broad range of occupiers
+ Flexible lease terms available from 5 years 
+ Fantastic parking ratio of 1:30, with a mix of basement and external
+ Low outgoings

Fit out includes:
+ Sit-to-stand workstations
+ Board room, meeting rooms and training rooms designed around the core
+ Collaboration areas, two kitchens/breakout areas 
+ Exclusive use end of trip facilities
+ Layout lends itself to be easily adapted
